overview: IMPACT Wrestling presents One Night Only: New Beginnings, in partnership with Pennsylvania Premiere Wrestling, from Holy Family Academy in Hazleton, Pennsylvania. In the main event, IMPACT World Champion Johnny Impact goes one-on-one with former champion Eli Drake. Plus Sami Callihan takes on Rich Swann, former best friends collide yet again when Eddie Edwards battles Moose in a Philly Street Fight, KM faces DeSean Pratt, Fallah Bahh meets Evander James and âThe Smoke Show" Scarlett Bordeaux steps into the ring against Christina Marie.
